{"tid":653484,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實劉馬車個朋友伍玉龍先係真正嘅幕後玩家","createTime":"2018-05-04T18:18:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T19:04:42.000Z","uid":52582,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5a97b954abf7f1c0af3eff76f050fd9a20882a4d","tid":653484,"uid":52582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T18:18:59.000Z","msg":"是咁的，自從有傳劉馬車咗大陸坐監之後，依然有人不斷利用佢facebook 去宣傳呢個伍玉龍（玉兄弟）嘅post 。咁我非常之無聊啦，所以就睇返佢啲post，發現基本上依家啲post全部都係呢個伍玉龍利用劉馬車 facebook嚟宣傳自己。<br />\n<br />\n呢一種post基本上一個月都出幾次又係同一個template <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/020057_e09c880b185b344978fca95449cf9bfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F020057_e09c880b185b344978fca95449cf9bfe.jpg&h=8ed92863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/020124_20fb182591d6583fe7d4302dbe464d2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F020124_20fb182591d6583fe7d4302dbe464d2e.jpg&h=38013a04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/020244_da497db463c14506558489fca0c57f65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F020244_da497db463c14506558489fca0c57f65.jpg&h=1e077c96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開埋啲垃圾分身account搏冇人睇得出呀 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/020945_f54bf3e7b9da985f143c24133c997db6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F020945_f54bf3e7b9da985f143c24133c997db6.jpg&h=f6d1651d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/020953_524cbe0321b3ad6f4b1faf57f8f03c45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F020953_524cbe0321b3ad6f4b1faf57f8f03c45.jpg&h=8166ad8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利用劉馬車個頻道扮係劉馬車出post話佢係臥龍先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/020453_6881900055e270dcf405411946d1a688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F020453_6881900055e270dcf405411946d1a688.jpg&h=bdd86850&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n扮謙虛扮曬嘢咁樣，講到尾又係想借馬車響大陸坐緊監呢段時間用佢個youtube channel 去賺分紅,推高自己知名度。 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無人想睇你呀垃圾，寧願睇愛回家都唔睇你呀，你自己打飛機啦臥龍先生</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/021857_3b71bde96b138471beed69d264825548.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F021857_3b71bde96b138471beed69d264825548.jpg&h=0cb79537&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a419791bb1ba8a05a9ace845857419c2aae60d4","tid":653484,"uid":70411,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T18:21:46.000Z","msg":"咁你而家做緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 宣傳？"},{"pid":"7a6fa35a581fd3ccf9a32ebfd96b6916db32c464","tid":653484,"uid"